        "id": "mineru_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_034_4",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "Whether you are a seasoned saver or are taking your first steps into the world of investment, Clare Francis, director of savings and investments at Barclays Smart Investor, above, has tips to hel grow a handy pot of cash:",
        "bbox": [
          0.03110512935546583,
