  {
    "eu_id": "EU-0002",
    "kind": "section_text_panel",
    "page": "newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_034",
    "primary_id": "mineru_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_034_6",
    "source": "header_anchor",
    "member_count": 7,
    "elements": [
      {
        "id": "mineru_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_034_6",
        "observed_type": "title",
        "canon_role": "section_header",
        "text": "Create and stick to a budget",
        "bbox": [
          0.032899656049050395,
          0.31651969429747207,
          0.18184537161656947,
          0.34332745443856555
        ],
        "order": 8
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_034_7",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "\"The importance of a wel-structured budget really cannot be overstated,\" says Clare.",
        "bbox": [
          0.03110512935546583,
          0.34379776601998824,
          0.21055779871392252,
          0.37295708406819517
        ],
        "order": 9
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_034_8",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "She suggests reviewing your monthly income and outgoings to identify areas where you can cut back on non-essential spending.",
        "bbox": [
          0.03110512935546583,
          0.37389770723104054,
          0.21115597427845073,
          0.41246325690770136
        ],
        "order": 10
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_034_9",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "\"The money you save can be used to pay off debts, moved into a savings account, or even invested for your future, Clare adds.",
        "bbox": [
          0.03170330491999402,
          0.41293356848912405,
          0.21115597427845073,
          0.4514991181657848
        ],
        "order": 11
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_034_10",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "\"By taking a proactive approach to your budgeting, you not only ensure that every pound is working as hard as possible for you, but that you also cultivate a mindset for long-term fi nancial success.\"",
        "bbox": [
          0.03050695379093764,
          0.45243974132863024,
          0.21115597427845073,
          0.5102880658436214
        ],
        "order": 12
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_034_11",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "There are plenty of free budgeting tools available online that could help, such as the budget planner from the government-backed MoneyHelper service at moneyhelper.org.uk.",
        "bbox": [
          0.02990877822640945,
          0.510758377425044,
          0.2117541498429789,
          0.5601410934744268
        ],
        "order": 13
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_034_12",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "It takes about 10 minutes to complete and can give you a fresh outlook and new understanding of your cash.",
        "bbox": [
          0.03110512935546583,
          0.5606114050558495,
          0.21115597427845073,
          0.599647266313933
        ],
        "order": 14
      }
    ]
  },
