        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "\"You don't need to have all your life gls e, a rough idea of what youre aiming for and how much money you'll need is helpful, says Clare.",
        "bbox": [
          0.03050695379093764,
          0.6330393885949441,
          0.2117541498429789,
          0.6819517930629042
        ],
        "order": 16
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_034_15",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "\"It provides a useful starting point to weigh up the best options available to you\"",
        "bbox": [
          0.03050695379093764,
          0.6824221046443268,
          0.21115597427845073,
          0.7106407995296884
        ],
        "order": 17
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_034_16",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "Many people keep all their cash in savings accounts.",
        "bbox": [
          0.03110512935546583,
          0.7115814226925338,
          0.21115597427845073,
          0.7303938859494415
        ],
        "order": 18
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_034_18",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "But Clare suggests that if youve got money you can afford to put away for the longer term, perhaps for five years or more, then investing could be worth considering.",
        "bbox": [
          0.02990877822640945,
          0.7313345091122869,
          0.2117541498429789,
          0.7797766019988243
        ],
        "order": 19
      },
      {
