        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "Financial Conduct Authorityhas a warning list of firms on its website as well as a financial services register of firms and people involved in regulated activities (fca.org.uk).",
        "bbox": [
          0.7871990429190967,
          0.7463844797178131,
