  {
    "eu_id": "EU-0007",
    "kind": "section_text_panel",
    "page": "newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_034",
    "primary_id": "mineru_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_034_42",
    "source": "header_anchor",
    "member_count": 6,
    "elements": [
      {
        "id": "mineru_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_034_42",
        "observed_type": "title",
        "canon_role": "section_header",
        "text": "5 Regular and investin",
        "bbox": [
          0.7889935696126813,
          0.8023515579071134,
          0.8918797667115298,
          0.8423280423280424
        ],
        "order": 28
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_034_37",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "She also warns that, with many investment scams starting on social media, it is important to \"sense check\" any information that is being shared online.",
        "bbox": [
          0.598175564528189,
          0.8075249853027631,
          0.7800209361447585,
          0.8564373897707231
        ],
        "order": 29
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_034_31",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "\"So, all you need to do is to pick a fund with a level of risk that youre comfortable with.\"",
        "bbox": [
          0.4097502617018095,
          0.8089359200470312,
          0.5892029310602662,
          0.8380952380952381
        ],
        "order": 30
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_034_26",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "Choosing where and how to invest money can feel daunting, which may for soe ea ae toi some o heir money from cash savin into investments.",
        "bbox": [
          0.2189322566173172,
          0.8150499706055262,
          0.40077762823388663,
          0.8653733098177543
        ],
        "order": 31
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_034_20",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "But people putting money into investments will need to be comfort- able with the risks and be aware that they could potentially get less money back than they put in.",
        "bbox": [
          0.03050695379093764,
          0.8197530864197531,
          0.2117541498429789,
          0.8686654908877132
        ],
        "order": 32
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_034_43",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "\"Just as saving monthl is a good habit to get into, so is investing regularly, says Clare.",
        "bbox": [
          0.7883953940481532,
          0.8432686654908877,
          0.8912815911470017,
          0.8818342151675485
        ],
        "order": 33
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "eu_id": "EU-0008",
    "kind": "section_text_panel",
    "page": "newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_034",
    "primary_id": "mineru_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_034_32",
    "source": "header_anchor",
    "member_count": 9,
    "elements": [
      {
        "id": "mineru_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_034_32",
        "observed_type": "title",
        "canon_role": "section_header",
        "text": "Look for financial guidance from reputable sources",
        "bbox": [
          0.40915208613728127,
          0.8442092886537331,
          0.585613877673097,
          0.8860670194003527
        ],
        "order": 34
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_034_38",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "Consider whether claims about high investment returns, for example, seem too good to be true.",
        "bbox": [
          0.5993719156572453,
          0.8573780129335685,
          0.7782264094511739,
          0.8870076425631981
        ],
        "order": 35
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_034_27",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "\"Many people face a choice paralysis, where they are afraid of making the wrong decision, and it prevents them from taking the next step,\" Clare explains.",
        "bbox": [
          0.27037535516674144,
          0.8658436213991769,
          0.40077762823388663,
          0.9363903586125808
        ],
        "order": 36
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_034_21",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "Analysis by Barclays indi- cates that many savers could be missing out on potentially higher returns.",
        "bbox": [
          0.03050695379093764,
          0.8696061140505585,
          0.15971287572902648,
          0.9081716637272192
        ],
        "order": 37
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_034_22",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "6 Pound cost averaging can help smooth out overall returns and reduce the risk",
        "bbox": [
          0.16689098250336473,
          0.8700764256319812,
          0.262599072827875,
          0.962257495590829
        ],
        "order": 38
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_034_44",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "\"Many people think you need a large amount before you can start, but that's not the case.\"",
        "bbox": [
          0.7883953940481532,
          0.8832451499118166,
          0.8870943621953044,
          0.9307466196355085
        ],
        "order": 39
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_034_33",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "Clare says: \"Our recent research found that a quarter of Brits are now turning to social media, community messaging apps and online forums for information about investing.\"",
        "bbox": [
          0.4085539105727531,
          0.8865373309817755,
          0.5903992821893226,
          0.9368606701940035
        ],
        "order": 40
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_034_39",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "It is crucial to keep in mind as well that fraudsters may use deepfake videos or other bogus information to give the false impression that an investment scheme has been endorsed by celebrities.",
        "bbox": [
          0.598175564528189,
          0.8874779541446208,
          0.7794227605802303,
          0.9472075249853028
        ],
        "order": 41
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_034_23",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "It estimates that 13 million UK adults hold £430billion of \"possible investments\" in cash savings, so they could be missing out on a lot of extra money if only they felt more confident and empowered to invest.",
        "bbox": [
          0.03050695379093764,
          0.908641975308642,
          0.16031105129355466,
          0.9679012345679012
        ],
        "order": 42
      }
    ]
  },
